Sentencas: In order to study the reaction area of the cathode of solid oxide fuel cells, the changes in microstructure of the cathode with a current-flow treatment were investigated.
Titulo: Effect of current-flow treatment on the microstructure and polarization change of cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Cathode samples (La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 + 10 mass% ZrO2) with two different microstructures were prepared.
Titulo: Effect of current-flow treatment on the microstructure and polarization change of cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Decrease of cathodic polarization by the current flow treatment was observed.
Titulo: Effect of current-flow treatment on the microstructure and polarization change of cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The observations of microstructure change of the cathode suggested that the movement of oxygen ion and vacancy took place at boundary between electrolyte and cathode.
Titulo: Effect of current-flow treatment on the microstructure and polarization change of cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The reason of decrease of cathodic polarization by current-dow treatment was discussed.
Titulo: Effect of current-flow treatment on the microstructure and polarization change of cathode of solid oxide fuel cells
